data.description: Stunning like new 4/2 home in Lemoore! This beautiful Woodside home is ready for a new owner to move right in. The open concept living space is the perfect set up for entertaining. The kitchen features a large granite center island with room to pull up a chair and enjoy a meal.  Stainless appliances, pantry, decorative and modern backsplash and a large space for a dining table. The three spare bedrooms are spacious, tile floors everywhere except the bedrooms and the laundry room is perfectly placed close to the bedrooms. The primary suite features a soaking tub, stand alone shower and a walk in closet. The backyard has a large concrete patio, the perfect are for a outdoor fire pit and the extra space on the side offers the potential for RV Parking!
